<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="container-fluid min-vh-100 bg-light px-0">
        <div class="row g-0 flex-nowrap">
            
            <aside class="col-12 col-md-3 col-xl-2 bg-dark min-vh-100">
                <%- include('partials/sidebar') %>
            </aside>

            <main class="col-12 col-md-9 col-xl-10 p-4" style="overflow-x: hidden;">
                
                <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm mb-4 border-start border-4 border-warning">
                    <h1 class="h2 mb-2 fw-bold text-dark">Panel de Control General</h1>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">Bienvenido al sistema de administración.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="row g-4">
                    
                    <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
                        <div class="card border-0 bg-primary text-white shadow-sm h-100">
                            <div class="card-body p-4">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-3">
                                    <div>
                                        <h6 class="text-uppercase mb-1 fw-semibold" style="font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.85; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Total Productos en BD</h6>
                                        <h2 class="display-5 mb-0 fw-bold"><%= totalProducts %></h2>
                                    </div>
                                    <i class="bi bi-database display-3 opacity-50"></i>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="row g-2 pt-3 border-top border-white border-opacity-25">
                                    <div class="col-6">
                                        <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded p-2 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
                                            <span class="small text-white-50"><i class="bi bi-eye-fill text-info me-1"></i> Activos:</span>
                                            <span class="fw-bold bg-success px-2 py-0.5 rounded small"><%= activeProducts %></span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-6">
                                        <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded p-2 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
                                            <span class="small text-white-50"><i class="bi bi-eye-slash-fill text-warning me-1"></i> Inactivos:</span>
                                            <span class="fw-bold bg-secondary px-2 py-0.5 rounded small"><%= inactiveProducts %></span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-footer bg-black bg-opacity-10 border-0 py-2.5">
                                <a href="/admin/productos" class="text-white text-decoration-none small d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
                                    <span>Ir a gestionar catálogo</span> <i class="bi bi-arrow-right-short fs-5"></i>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
                        <div class="card border-0 bg-success text-white shadow-sm h-100 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                            <div class="card-body p-4 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
                                <div>
                                    <h6 class="text-uppercase mb-2 fw-semibold" style="font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.85; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Conexión MySQL</h6>
                                    <h3 class="h3 mb-0 fw-bold d-flex align-items-center gap-2 m-0">
                                        <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-white"></i> ONLINE
                                    </h3>
                                </div>
                                <i class="bi bi-cpu fs-1 opacity-50"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-footer bg-black bg-opacity-10 border-0 py-3 mt-auto">
                                <span class="text-white-50 small">Sincronizado con Sequelize</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="card mt-4 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-header bg-white fw-bold py-3 border-bottom text-secondary">
                        <i class="bi bi-info-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Información del sistema
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body text-secondary p-4">
                        <p class="fw-semibold">Funcionalidades activas:</p>
                        <ul class="mb-0 ps-3">
                            <li class="mb-2.5"><strong>Gestión de productos:</strong> El administrador podrá gestionar productos: creando, actualizando y eliminando en tiempo real.</li>
                            <li class="mb-2.5"><strong>Visualización en BD:</strong> Monitoreo directo de la cantidad de registros persistidos de manera segura.</li>
                            <li><strong>Información de logs:</strong> Historial centralizado para auditar las acciones del sistema.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </main>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>